caption: #contest Hi! My Name is Maor I was born in NYC but now live in Cali. I'm 14 years old and you guys are my idols.. You guys have changed my life in so many positive ways. All I want to do is say Thank you in person. You guys taught me that's it's okay to be me. I love to sing and because of you guys I started putting myself out there.. I started to sing in public and not really care about what other people thought about me. Thank you guys for being you. You guys have put such a positive affect on me. Love you ? ~Maor
